WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.500
Open the real Camino page in TYPO3's Visual Editor.

00:03.500 --> 00:10.500
Select the headline and change it to "100 Kilometers of Fun".

00:10.500 --> 00:14.500
Click "Save 1 change" to persist the edit in TYPO3.

00:14.500 --> 00:19.700
The saved headline is immediately visible on the frontend.
